methods.getNext:
Get the next node after the input node.

:param node: (IntrusiveDoublyLinkedNode.Adapter.NODE_TYPE) - The input node
:return: (IntrusiveDoublyLinkedNode.Adapter.NODE_TYPE) The input node's next node
methods.getPrev:
Get the previous node before the input node.

:param node: (IntrusiveDoublyLinkedNode.Adapter.NODE_TYPE) - The input node
:return: (IntrusiveDoublyLinkedNode.Adapter.NODE_TYPE) The input node's previous node
methods.setNext:

methods.setPrev:
